properties.areaDesc: Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 20-60 nm; Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 8 at 3:25AM EST until January 12 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Melbourne FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...East winds increasing to 20 to 25 kt beginning tonight,
becoming southeast and gusting to 30 to 35 kt. Seas building to
7 to 10 feet.

* WHERE...Volusia-Brevard County Line to Sebastian Inlet 20-60
nm and Sebastian Inlet to Jupiter Inlet 20-60 nm.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 4 AM Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Wind and wave conditions will be hazardous for small craft.
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in these conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 4 AM SUNDAY
